  "description_long": "University Of Florida/Florida Cooperative Extension - Holmes County Cooperative Extension Service is a HUD-approved housing counseling agency in Bonifay, FL. As a federally approved organization, they provide free or low-cost counseling on housing, mortgage, and credit issues. Services include Financial/Budget Counseling, Fair Housing/Lending Assistance, Home Improvement/Rehabilitation, Non-Delinquency Post-Purchase Counseling. HUD-approved agencies must meet federal standards for counselor training and service quality.",
